text: Kochkar () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Voskresensky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 32 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Meleuz, 7 km from Voskresenskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Kochkar
